author: bald and bankrupt
description:
🇮🇳I continued my trip across West Bengal travelling like the poorest of locals on the infamous 'general class' compartment of the railway network. It was at times horrifying and at times enlightening. Good people. Terrible conditions. And the question I ask you is 'are you mental enough to visit India?' Because you have to be mental to visit.
I travelled with @BackpackerBen so watch his video of our trip to see his perspective.

www.mrbaldandbankrupt.com for my books
title: India...I Have To Tell You What I Think
